Here are 10 User Story Requirements for the WorkflowManager
__________________________________________________________
Identifier    |  User Story
__________________________________________________________
   ALL  |  As a user I put an assignment on a calendar.
   PM   |  As a user, I can create a project.
   PM   |  As a project leader, I can break a project down into smaller steps.
   PM   |  As a project leader, I can assign project members to different project steps.
   OH   |  As a project leader, I can assign due dates for project steps.
   OH   |  As a user, I can view the assigned steps and due dates.
   OH   |  As a project leader, I can lock project steps from project members.
   SC   |  As a user, I can view the status of my assigned projects.
   SC   |  As a user, I can view dependencies within the project pipeline.
   SC   |  As a user, I can select my profile so the system can determine my roles and permissions.
